title: My Friend Masupilami
lyrics: Hoobah, Hoobah You're the king! You're the one, you're the best Marsupilami! In the jungle with the rest, Marsupilami! Up and down all around, Marsupilami! Now come and dance! Come and dance with me! Hoobah, Hoobah, Marsupilami Hoobah, Hoobah, Marsupilami Hoobah, Hoobah, Marsupilami Hoobah, Hoobah
